<figcaption class="quarto-float-caption-bottom quarto-float-caption quarto-float-fig" id="fig-budget-revenue-correlation-caption-0ceaefa1-69ba-4598-a22c-09a6ac19f8ca">
Figure 4: Scatter plot of inflation-adjusted movie budget vs. worldwide gross revenue
</figcaption>
