<span id="cb10-547"><a href="#cb10-547" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="in">```python</span></span>
<span id="cb10-548"><a href="#cb10-548" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#| label: fig-top-rated-countries</span></span>
<span id="cb10-549"><a href="#cb10-549" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#| fig-cap: &quot;Origin countries of top-rated movies (IMDb Rating &gt;= 8.0)&quot;</span></span>
