&lt;figcaption class=&quot;quarto-float-caption-bottom quarto-float-caption quarto-float-fig&quot; id=&quot;fig-genre-trends-caption-0ceaefa1-69ba-4598-a22c-09a6ac19f8ca&quot;&gt;
Figure 1: Proportion of top 5 film genres for each decade from 1990 to 2020s
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
